des: Open up a Case O Riddles. This skill is meant to challenge your mind by giving you a simple riddle to solve, with an entertaining answer. When using the skill, you can say "Alexa, next" to move to the next riddle. At any point, you can say "Alexa, stop" to exit the skill. This skill was created using a Skill Blueprint. Your requests to this skill are not shared with the skill developer.
